Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:03.44,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're\Na human and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.50,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.70,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.76,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You've matured splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.39,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Just the way I wanted you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.13,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:12.31,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.40,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,All of the battles you've fought
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.60,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,were a part of my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:40.20,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako... Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.04,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.98,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.11,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.28,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.13,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,A Zanpakuto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.58,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,and a Hollow mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.95,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.50,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Visored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.52,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.53,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:23.27,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.04,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:41.15,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the Visored have made\Ncontact with Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.46,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.03,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:50.43,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Call Ulquiorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.36,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have him go to the\NWorld of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.37,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.55,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hirako...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:02.43,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Still a prudent man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Tensa Zangetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.60,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,Orange hair and a black Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:27.15,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it. He's\Nour target, Yammy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.97,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,I saved us the trouble\Nof searching, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.66,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Suerte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.75,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:55.65,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,You need to resort to your\NZanpakuto for a foe like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.31,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,I said, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.94,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:03.28,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that sword at his waist\Nis a Zanpakuto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:07.00,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The cracked Hollow mask...\NThe hole in his chest...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:08.29,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Zanpakuto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.10,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I was heading over here,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.24,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought the Spiritual Pressure felt odd.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.11,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are these two?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.03,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are they like us?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.29,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like Hirako and me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.93,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! I can't\Nmove my body!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:37.31,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I deny you... So now\Nyou'll get in my way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.11,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.49,B2,YAMMY,0000,0000,0000,,Break apart and disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.05,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:01.17,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.31,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is done for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.78,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,I shall inform Lord Aizen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:13.20,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,that the wannabe Soul Reaper\Nhe had his eyes on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.03,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,was trash that wasn't\Neven worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.86,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you knew\Nwhere we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.31,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:44.21,B2,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,That face looks like you've finally\Ndecided to become one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.74,B2,ULQUIORRA,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.98,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,He finally mastered\NHollowfication?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.61,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,The speed of his development\Nis wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.88,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:21.83,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.95,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.42,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have made\Nall preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.83,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.04,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:33.23,B2,TOSEN,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.84,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.18,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave the rest to Ulquiorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.04,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.89,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.73,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:51.47,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:57.05,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will...protect you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:04.92,B2,ULQUIORRA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's impossible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.32,B2,ULQUIORRA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With his bare hands?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.03,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,All of the battles...I've fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:48.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,were according...to your plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.67,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.63,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you what\Nyou mean by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.64,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:18.40,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't raise your voice,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.36,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to\Nbe surprised about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.78,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:29.50,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,believed that you would be\Na great research subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:33.75,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,so I assisted your development.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.30,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.27,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You never thought\Nit was strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:48.57,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You had never seen a Hollow\Nin your life before you met
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:52.28,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki, but shortly after doing so,\Nyou were attacked by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:58.01,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,How a Menos Grande was\Ndrawn to bait that Quincies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.90,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,use to attract and exterminate\Nminor Hollows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.12,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,When you began to get used\Nto fighting as a Soul Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:10.79,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia Kuchiki's previously undetected\NSpiritual Pressure was suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.50,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,detected and reported\Nto Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:20.67,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You fought Renji Abarai,\NKenpachi Zaraki, Byakuya Kuchiki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:28.10,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,when your power was\Ncomparable to theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.60,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You never once thought\Nit was strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.55,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that\Nyou met by fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.23,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.94,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that attack\Nhappened by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:49.05,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think your victories were\Nthe result of your hard work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.38,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.88,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Your power should be much\Ngreater than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.00,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you believe what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.48,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,All of my battles were\Nyour doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.48,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You planned all of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.94,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:28.92,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that you\Ndiscovered Rukia after
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:31.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,she had gone missing in\Nthe World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:36.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you say that you knew about\Nme since the time I met her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.42,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.12,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,What an interesting thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:47.10,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You just called me a liar and said\Nthat you would never believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.81,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You claim that I'm\Nlying right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:56.85,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,So why do you think I was\Ntelling the truth back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.26,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:05.90,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I sympathize with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:10.05,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,This world was never\Nabout truth or lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:13.71,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,There are only hard facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.82,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.38,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,everyone who exists in this\Nworld mistakenly believes that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:23.92,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,only facts that are favorable\Nto them are truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.38,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,They know no other way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:36.20,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,But for the powerless who make\Nup most of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:41.86,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,facts that act against them\Nare the only truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.82,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know all of the facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:53.78,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Who stationed Rukia Kuchiki\Nin the World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.20,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave Renji Abarai's equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.26,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,the ability to detect\NSpiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.25,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Who added information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:08.76,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,on your whereabouts in the report\Nsent to the Lieutenants?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:15.76,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Was I really unable to figure\Nout where the Hogyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.35,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,was for over a hundred years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:35.57,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you believed that I\Nwould be a great research subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What did you base that belief on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:45.62,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If you saw me when\NI met Rukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,When did you believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.30,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Quit talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.00,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.54,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you it was\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:08.02,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew about you since\Nyou were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.74,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:16.66,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You were special from the\Nmoment you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.16,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're\Na human and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.00,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.07,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.39,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're\Na human and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.76,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Human and what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.30,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His last word was drowned\Nout by the noise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.24,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I lost my\Nchance to hear it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:17:00.81,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was mistaken.\NI never needed to hear it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.71,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer soon appeared\Nbefore my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:29.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.93,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.24,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping his distance, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.05,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,A wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:58.10,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's in their blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.70,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.61,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you want to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.36,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:23.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I know I have to be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I was telling you I\Ncouldn't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:28.37,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.75,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long you stare,\Nyou're not imaging things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.97,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:48.52,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,There are probably tons of things\Nyou want to ask me, but all of it-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.29,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anything\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You probably had your reasons\Nfor not telling me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.86,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.71,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to\Nask you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know a good way\Nof asking you about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:15.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,that without trampling\Non your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.01,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Until you feel like telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:26.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Until you feel the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, you don't\Nneed to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:36.61,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've learned\Nsome tact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I picked it up from someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Someone told me\Nsomething similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:43.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It helped make me\Nfeel a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:52.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for hitting me, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I've come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:01.88,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.10,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hit you, I headbutted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:08.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.69,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,He hid his Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:30.33,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,He placed a pretty\Npowerful barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.88,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,You've been watching\Nfor quite a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.55,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.42,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't just been watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:47.43,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't find an opportunity\Nor a need to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:49.93,B2,AIZEN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:39.02,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since\NI've fought you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:46.50,B2,GIN,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I won't\Nbe holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:22.96,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ichigo. You sure you\Ndon't want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:23.71,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:24.33,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:24.87,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:28.71,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You don't want to know what\Nhappened in your dad's past?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:29.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:32.43,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?\NCome on, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted me to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.31,B2,RYUKEN,0000,0000,0000,,Quincy Encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:44.29,B2,RYUKEN,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, if you have time to be lazing\Nabout, then help me with my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:46.83,B2,RYUKEN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.82,B2,RYUKEN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:56.60,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I've got some business to attend to.\NSorry! From Isshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.13,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some business\Nto attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:23:55.11,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.11,0:23:56.09,B2,ISSHIN,0000,0000,0000,,From Isshin.